data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ASSUMABLE FOR VA LOAN AT 3.1% with Secondary Mortgage Lender Available!! $2,000 Credit towards Closing Costs or Rate Buy Down! Stunningly Renovated 3 Bed, 2 Bath home with Fenced in Backyard on a Serene Tree-Lined Street. This perfect location in Port of Tampa offers a blend of modern elegance and timeless charm. NO HOA. NO CDD!     Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting open floor plan that will take your breath away.    The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, boasting exquisite wood cabinets paired with stunning granite countertops. Prepare your favorite meals in a space that's as beautiful as it is functional with extra storage in the convenient island. Both bathrooms also feature the same luxurious granite countertops, creating a seamless and cohesive design aesthetic.    The bedrooms are generously sized, ensuring that everyone in the family has a comfortable and inviting space to call their own. The master suite is an absolute showstopper, offering an ensuite bathroom that's designed to pamper and impress. It's a retreat you'll never want to leave!    Located in an area that's bustling with new construction, this home is poised in a neighborhood on the rise. It's the perfect time to invest in a property surrounded by the promise of growth & so close to the water.    The location is unbeatable! Situated near MacDill military base, you'll find yourself conveniently close to downtown Tampa, Gandy Bridge, Gadsen Park, and all the exciting amenities that this vibrant city has to offer. Close to Picnic Island Park; A Beach, Dog Park, & Disc Golf Haven for you and your furry family! Less than 10 Miles from Raymond James Stadium & TPA Airport.     Best of all, this incredible home is available at an amazing price. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this move in ready home yours. All information deemed reliable but to be verified by buyer and buyers agent. Schedule a viewing today and let your dream of owning a beautifully updated home become a reality!
